        <t:abstract><t:p>An apocryphal work formed by the merger of two original writings: (1) an apocalypse of Jesus to the Apostles in
        Galilee (chapters 1-11 in the edition) and (2) the so-called Epistula Apostolorum (chapters 12-62 in the edition).</t:p></t:abstract>
